{"tid":402290,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人發現Spotify,KKBOX好多英文歌唔見咗","createTime":"2017-09-16T10:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T06:59:27.000Z","uid":127176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"af345500279453d21d0b219fde36f8b30bea37ca","tid":402290,"uid":127176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"之前用開Spotify，依家用緊KKBOX<br />\n轉果陣要重新加過哂d歌，加完覺得唔係好對路，結果發現Spotify playlist入面歌嘅實際數量少過佢顯示嘅數字，又發現真係有d當初明明有嘅歌消失咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢d歌依家係KKBOX都係冇<br />\n我個Playlist入面總共應該有8首唔見咗<br />\n已知嘅有:<br />\nBeggin' - Madcon<br />\nWading - Jhene Aiko<br />\nMake Me Feel Better - Alex Adair<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有發現同樣嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa5cb79e2b26471ade04ed1e124889f7c54ab62","tid":402290,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"俾人買左版權？"},{"pid":"0e12386b94e00c111d89fee8065bce861db85fdd","tid":402290,"uid":127176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾人買左版權？</blockquote><br />\n我都有諗過<br />\n但見同一個人其他歌都冇事<br />\n如果真係個artist或者公司要求收番嘅話，應該會好似之前TS咁乜都冇哂"},{"pid":"e0fda34f7a842e03a036ac23f22d73d699386dde","tid":402290,"uid":127176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c548327cd8ac869a1e8b8df42e8052c18de938","tid":402290,"uid":127176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}